    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like there's no point to any of it. every single day is just a struggle to get through the next hour. sometimes i find myself thinking about him, and how much more peaceful it would be if i could just be with him again. like, if the pain finally stopped and i didn't have to carry this weight anymore. it almost feels like the only way to actually find some peace.",
